name: Great Game - Planet of the Apes

metadata.name: Great Game - Leader Joker 007
metadata.description: Leader Joker (Bo Joker), not a king, but a manager of His Highness and wants to rule the Parallel Metaverse, although he has left several alliances. Suffering from delusions of grandeur and a very disheveled and shabby figure. He has excellent oratorical qualities and a beautiful spoken language. Lover of closed holidays in forbidden times. A quarrelsome Joker often confuses cards. One of the weighty figures in the Parallel Metaverse.
